    {
      "raw": "Consent is implied in an emergency situation. ( Cobbs, supra, 8 Cal. 3d at p.\n243.)",
      "statutes": [],
      "cases": []
    },
    {
      "raw": "This defense is considered a \"justiﬁcation.\" Justiﬁcation for failure to disclose is\nan affirmative defense on which the defendant has the burden of proof. ( Mathis\nv. Morrissey (1992) 11 Cal. App.4th 332, 347, fn. 9 [13 Cal. Rptr.2d 819].)",
      "statutes": [],
      "cases": [
